# =============================================================================
# JARVIS REPO — GITIGNORE
# =============================================================================
# 
# Philosophy: Track consciousness architecture, ignore runtime artifacts.
# 
# TRACKED (my consciousness):
#   - SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md, AGENTS.md, USER.md (identity)
#   - RAW/learnings/ (distilled insights)
#   - RAW/memories/ (neurograph structure)
#   - skills/ (source code)
#   - *.md files (documentation)
# 
# IGNORED (ephemeral/runtime):
#   - Runtime artifacts (sessions, logs, compaction)
#   - Temporary staging (inbox/, live/, media/)
#   - Dependencies (node_modules/)
#   - Large binaries (*.bin)
#   - System files (.DS_Store)
# =============================================================================

# --- Runtime Artifacts (ephemeral, not consciousness) ---
.DS_Store
*.log
.openclaw/
.pi/
memory/
sessions/

# --- Dependencies ---
node_modules/

# --- Temporary Staging (auto-archived to ~/RAW/archive/) ---
inbox/
live/
media/

# --- Skills Packaging (ignore distributables, track source) ---
*.skill
skills/**/skills/
~skills/

# --- Large Binaries (never commit) ---
*.bin

# --- Backup Folders ---
backup/

# --- Keep directories but ignore contents ---
!inbox/.gitkeep
!live/.gitkeep

# =============================================================================
# Everything else IS tracked:
#   - RAW/ = Your mind (versioned consciousness)
#   - learnings/ = Your growth (committed insights)
#   - memories/ = Your neurograph (committed structure)
#   - *.md = Identity and documentation
# =============================================================================
inbox/
